{"tid":805120,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"九陰真經 國際服(私服)","createTime":"2018-09-03T13:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T03:35:00.000Z","uid":99856,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"aaa712a74c9d62eca77e6a1f4573c2a0673e3a55","tid":805120,"uid":99856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T13:52:36.000Z","msg":"〖九陰真經〗國際服<br />\n九陰國際服已經開超過一個月，有十倍修為轉換、十倍內修，商城有賣所有風物志，99武學，奇珍異寶，兵錄等。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">RC 27809688</span></strong>，等着你的加入!!!<br />\n目前5內九陰志，同步官方雪域逃殺版本  <br />\n充值１比１０　（官方１比１）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講個SER大約40% 越南仔 40%大陸其餘兩成係香港台灣 <br />\n可以買帳號但係自己打造一隻都好簡單(因為佢係台服,國服平十倍) <br />\n一蚊人民幣=五十萬修為轉化 內修速度係平時十倍 基本上兩三日都已經封頂 <br />\n<ins>依家大約30個香港人 已經入左去屠殺緊D越南,大陸仔</ins><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/212839_321532365639f31b3b9f8ea8be0c6be2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F212839_321532365639f31b3b9f8ea8be0c6be2.png&h=08cdddb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/212839_d383b2fd1d6fe8472a4296bd24e41670.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F212839_d383b2fd1d6fe8472a4296bd24e41670.png&h=7ea16867&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/212840_f7bd9b0dfb0865d763286b1df031d160.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F212840_f7bd9b0dfb0865d763286b1df031d160.png&h=90d56d33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一蚊等於十蚊咁用之前出過 99金武學 風物誌都有"},{"pid":"1664dd313ac882977c9d5823719fc1421a01ed30","tid":805120,"uid":99856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T13:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5c462e1f18eebb6ab7e99336bd7492850c359d","tid":805120,"uid":156527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":